<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Semetra – Der smarte Studienplaner für FH-Studenten</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Semetra hilft FH-Studierenden, Module zu verwalten, Lernziele zu verfolgen und Prüfungen im Blick zu behalten. Kostenlos starten." />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#7C3AED" />

  <!-- Open Graph -->
  <meta property="og:title" content="Semetra – Studienplaner für FH-Studenten" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Organisiere dein Studium. Module, Aufgaben, Prüfungen – alles an einem Ort." />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://semetra.ch" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --accent:      #7C3AED;
      --accent-lt:   #EDE9FE;
      --accent-dk:   #5B21B6;
      --accent-glow: rgba(124,58,237,0.22);
      --text:        #0F0A1E;
      --muted:       #6B6880;
      --border:      #E8E4F4;
      --bg:          #FAFAFA;
      --white:       #FFFFFF;
      --radius:      16px;
      --radius-sm:   10px;
      --shadow:      0 4px 24px rgba(15,10,30,0.08);
      --shadow-lg:   0 12px 48px rgba(15,10,30,0.12);
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    nav {
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 5vw;
      height: 64px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .nav-logo {
      font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .nav-logo span { color: var(--text); }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2rem; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a { color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; font-size: .9rem; font-weight: 500; transition: color .2s; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
    .nav-cta {
      background: var(--accent); color: white;
      padding: 9px 22px; border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: .875rem;
      transition: background .2s, box-shadow .2s;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px var(--accent-glow);
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--accent-dk); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(124,58,237,.38); }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 108px 5vw 96px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 50% -10%, rgba(124,58,237,0.13) 0%, transparent 70%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #F7F4FF 0%, #ffffff 100%);
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; width: 600px; height: 600px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(124,58,237,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
      top: -200px; right: -100px; pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; width: 400px; height: 400px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(124,58,237,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
      bottom: -100px; left: -100px; pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
      background: var(--accent-lt); color: var(--accent);
      font-size: .78rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .5px;
      padding: 5px 16px; border-radius: 100px; margin-bottom: 28px;
      text-transform: uppercase; border: 1px solid rgba(124,58,237,.2);
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5.5vw, 3.8rem);
      font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -1.5px; max-width: 820px; margin-bottom: 22px;
    }
    .hero h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--accent); }
    .hero > p {
      font-size: 1.125rem; color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 520px; margin-bottom: 44px; line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--accent); color: white;
      padding: 15px 36px; border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem;
      transition: background .2s, transform .15s, box-shadow .2s;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(124,58,237,.40);
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--accent-dk); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 10px 32px rgba(124,58,237,.46); }
    .btn-secondary {
      background: var(--white); color: var(--accent);
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      padding: 15px 32px; border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem;
      transition: border-color .2s, background .2s;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--accent); background: var(--accent-lt); }

    /* Hero social proof */
    .hero-proof {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 6px; color: var(--muted); font-size: .83rem; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center;
    }
    .hero-avatars { display: flex; }
    .hero-avatars .av {
      width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%;
      border: 2px solid white; background: var(--accent-lt);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: .58rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent);
      margin-left: -8px;
    }
    .hero-avatars .av:first-child { margin-left: 0; }
    .hero-stars { color: #F59E0B; letter-spacing: -1px; font-size: .95rem; }

    /* ── TRUST BAND ── */
    .trust-band {
      display: flex; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
      background: var(--white);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .trust-item {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      padding: 18px 28px; font-size: .84rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--muted);
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .trust-item:last-child { border-right: none; }

    /* ── SECTION ── */
    section { padding: 88px 5vw; }
    .section-label {
      text-align: center; font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .section-title {
      text-align: center; font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.3rem);
      font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -.5px;
      margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.25;
    }
    .section-sub {
      text-align: center; color: var(--muted); font-size: .975rem;
      max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 64px; line-height: 1.65;
    }

    /* ── FEATURES GRID ── */
    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .feature-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 28px 24px;
      transition: box-shadow .25s, transform .25s, border-color .25s;
    }
    .feature-card:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(124,58,237,.12);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      border-color: rgba(124,58,237,.25);
    }
    .feature-icon {
      width: 46px; height: 46px;
      background: var(--accent-lt); border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.35rem; margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .feature-card h3 {
      font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .feature-card p { color: var(--muted); font-size: .875rem; line-height: 1.6; }
    .pro-badge {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7C3AED, #9B59B6);
      color: white; font-size: .63rem; font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: .4px; padding: 2px 9px; border-radius: 100px;
      text-transform: uppercase; white-space: nowrap;
    }

    /* ── HOW IT WORKS ── */
    .steps-section { background: var(--white); }
    .steps {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 40px; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;
    }
    .step-num {
      width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent); color: white;
      font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 900;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(124,58,237,.35);
    }
    .step h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .step p { color: var(--muted); font-size: .875rem; line-height: 1.6; }

    /* ── PRICING ── */
    #preise { background: linear-gradient(160deg, #F7F4FF 0%, #ffffff 100%); }
    .pricing-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 18px; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .pricing-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 32px 22px; position: relative;
      transition: box-shadow .25s, transform .25s;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    }
    .pricing-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .pricing-card.popular {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--accent), 0 8px 36px rgba(124,58,237,.15);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FDFBFF 0%, #FFFFFF 100%);
    }
    .popular-badge {
      position: absolute; top: -13px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #9B59B6);
      color: white; font-size: .68rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: .5px;
      padding: 4px 16px; border-radius: 100px; text-transform: uppercase; white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .savings-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #DCFCE7; color: #15803D;
      font-size: .68rem; font-weight: 700;
      padding: 2px 9px; border-radius: 100px; margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .plan-name {
      font-size: .78rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 4px; letter-spacing: .4px; text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .plan-price {
      font-size: 2.4rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -1.5px;
      line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .plan-price sup { font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: super; margin-right: 1px; }
    .plan-price span { font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--muted); }
    .plan-period { font-size: .78rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.5; }
    .plan-divider { height: 1px; background: var(--border); margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .plan-features { list-style: none; margin-bottom: 24px; flex: 1; }
    .plan-features li {
      font-size: .855rem; padding: 5px 0;
      display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px;
    }
    .plan-features li .check { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .plan-features li .dash { color: #D1D5DB; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .plan-features li.locked { color: #C0BDD4; }
    .plan-btn {
      display: block; text-align: center;
      padding: 13px; border-radius: 9px;
      font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: .9rem;
      transition: all .2s; margin-top: auto;
    }
    .plan-btn.primary {
      background: var(--accent); color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(124,58,237,.35);
    }
    .plan-btn.primary:hover { background: var(--accent-dk); transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(124,58,237,.45); }
    .plan-btn.outline { border: 2px solid var(--border); color: var(--accent); }
    .plan-btn.outline:hover { border-color: var(--accent); background: var(--accent-lt); }
    .pricing-note {
      text-align: center; margin-top: 32px; color: var(--muted); font-size: .81rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    /* ── TESTIMONIALS ── */
    #testimonials { background: var(--white); }
    .testimonials-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px; max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .testimonial-card {
      background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 30px 28px;
      position: relative;
      transition: box-shadow .25s, transform .25s;
    }
    .testimonial-card:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(124,58,237,.1);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .testimonial-card::before {
      content: '"';
      position: absolute; top: 16px; right: 22px;
      font-size: 4.5rem; line-height: 1; color: var(--accent-lt);
      font-family: Georgia, serif; font-weight: 900;
    }
    .testimonial-stars { color: #F59E0B; font-size: .9rem; margin-bottom: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; }
    .testimonial-card p { font-size: .875rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 22px; font-style: italic; }
    .testimonial-author { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
    .author-avatar {
      width: 38px; height: 38px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent-lt); color: var(--accent);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: .73rem; font-weight: 800; flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .author-name { font-size: .875rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .author-role { font-size: .78rem; color: var(--muted); }

    /* ── FAQ ── */
    #faq { background: #F7F4FF; }
    .faq-list { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .faq-item {
      background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm); margin-bottom: 10px; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .faq-question {
      width: 100%; text-align: left; padding: 20px 24px;
      background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
      font-size: .93rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text);
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
      font-family: inherit; transition: background .15s;
    }
    .faq-question:hover { background: var(--accent-lt); }
    .faq-icon {
      width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent-lt); color: var(--accent);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;
      transition: transform .3s, background .2s;
    }
    .faq-item.open .faq-icon { transform: rotate(45deg); background: var(--accent); color: white; }
    .faq-answer {
      max-height: 0; overflow: hidden;
      transition: max-height .35s ease;
      padding: 0 24px;
    }
    .faq-answer p { color: var(--muted); font-size: .875rem; line-height: 1.75; padding-bottom: 20px; }
    .faq-item.open .faq-answer { max-height: 220px; }

    /* ── CTA BAND ── */
    .cta-band {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5B21B6 0%, #7C3AED 50%, #8B5CF6 100%);
      color: white; text-align: center; padding: 96px 5vw;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .cta-band::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; width: 500px; height: 500px;
      border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      top: -200px; right: -100px;
    }
    .cta-band::after {
      content: ''; position: absolute; width: 300px; height: 300px;
      border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      bottom: -100px; left: -50px;
    }
    .cta-band h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem); font-weight: 900;
      margin-bottom: 12px; letter-spacing: -.5px; position: relative;
    }
    .cta-band p { font-size: 1rem; opacity: .85; margin-bottom: 36px; position: relative; }
    .btn-white {
      background: white; color: var(--accent);
      padding: 16px 42px; border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1rem;
      display: inline-block; position: relative;
      transition: transform .15s, box-shadow .2s;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.18);
    }
    .btn-white:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,.25); }
    .cta-sub { margin-top: 16px; font-size: .78rem; opacity: .65; position: relative; }

    /* ── LEGAL ── */
    #impressum { background: var(--white); }
    .legal-box {
      max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto;
      background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 36px 40px;
    }
    .legal-box h2 { font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .legal-box h3 {
      font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 24px 0 8px;
      color: var(--accent); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .6px;
    }
    .legal-box p, .legal-box address {
      font-size: .875rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.75; font-style: normal;
    }
    .legal-box a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer { background: #0F0A1E; color: #9B97B0; padding: 64px 5vw 32px; }
    .footer-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 40px; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto 52px;
    }
    .footer-brand { font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 900; color: white; margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: -.5px; }
    .footer-brand span { color: var(--accent); }
    .footer-tagline { font-size: .82rem; line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .footer-col h4 {
      color: white; font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 14px; letter-spacing: .6px; text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .footer-col a {
      display: block; color: #9B97B0; text-decoration: none;
      font-size: .82rem; margin-bottom: 9px; transition: color .2s;
    }
    .footer-col a:hover { color: white; }
    .footer-bottom {
      border-top: 1px solid #1E1933; padding-top: 28px;
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; font-size: .78rem;
    }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .pricing-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); }
    }
    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 560px) {
      .pricing-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .trust-item { padding: 14px 16px; font-size: .78rem; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ── NAV ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">Seme<span>tra</span></a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#funktionen">Funktionen</a></li>
    <li><a href="#preise">Preise</a></li>
    <li><a href="#testimonials">Stimmen</a></li>
    <li><a href="#download">Download</a></li>
    <li><a href="#impressum">Impressum</a></li>
  </ul>
  <a href="https://app.semetra.ch" class="nav-cta">Kostenlos starten →</a>
</nav>

<!-- ── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="hero">
  <span class="hero-badge">🎓 Für FH-Studierende in der Schweiz</span>
  <h1>Dein Studium.<br><em>Endlich im Griff.</em></h1>
  <p>Module, Aufgaben, Prüfungen und Lernziele – als Desktop-App <em>und</em> Web App. Mit Echtzeit-Sync zwischen allen Geräten.</p>
  <div class="hero-btns">
    <a href="https://app.semetra.ch" class="btn-primary">🚀 Web App starten — kostenlos</a>
    <a href="#download" class="btn-secondary">⬇ Desktop herunterladen</a>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-proof">
    <div class="hero-avatars">
      <div class="av">LK</div>
      <div class="av">MS</div>
      <div class="av">AB</div>
      <div class="av">TW</div>
      <div class="av" style="font-size:.65rem;">50+</div>
    </div>
    <span class="hero-stars">★★★★★</span>
    <span>Über 50 Studierende auf der Warteliste</span>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── TRUST BAND ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<div class="trust-band">
  <div class="trust-item"><span>💾</span><span>Desktop 100% Offline</span></div>
  <div class="trust-item"><span>🌐</span><span>Web App inklusive</span></div>
  <div class="trust-item"><span>🔄</span><span>Echtzeit-Sync</span></div>
  <div class="trust-item"><span>🇨🇭</span><span>Swiss Made</span></div>
  <div class="trust-item"><span>⚡</span><span>Konto sofort aktiv</span></div>
  <div class="trust-item"><span>↩️</span><span>14 Tage Rückgaberecht</span></div>
</div>

<!-- ── FUNKTIONEN ────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="funktionen">
  <p class="section-label">Was Semetra kann</p>
  <h2 class="section-title">Alles was du als FH-Student brauchst</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">15+ Features — von der Modulverwaltung bis zur KI-gestützten Prüfungsvorbereitung. Als Desktop-App und im Browser.</p>
  <div class="features-grid">

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">📚</div>
      <h3>Modulverwaltung</h3>
      <p>Erfasse all deine Module pro Semester inklusive ECTS, Code, Modultyp und Gewichtung. Mit Links zu Moodle, GitHub, SharePoint und Notizen.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🌐</div>
      <h3>Web App</h3>
      <p>Semetra läuft jetzt auch im Browser — auf jedem Gerät, ohne Installation. Melde dich an und habe dein Studium überall dabei.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🔄</div>
      <h3>Desktop ↔ Web Sync <span class="pro-badge">Pro</span></h3>
      <p>Arbeite auf dem Desktop und greife unterwegs per Browser zu. Deine Daten sind immer synchron — in Echtzeit via Cloud.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🎓</div>
      <h3>Studiengänge-Import <span class="pro-badge">Pro</span></h3>
      <p>Wähle deine Fachhochschule und deinen Studiengang — alle Pflichtmodule werden automatisch importiert. FFHS, ZHAW, FHNW, BFH, OST und mehr.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🏆</div>
      <h3>Credits &amp; ECTS-Tracking</h3>
      <p>Sieh deinen Fortschritt auf dem Weg zum Abschluss. Fortschrittsbalken, ECTS pro Semester und Gesamtübersicht auf einen Blick.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">✅</div>
      <h3>Aufgaben &amp; Deadlines</h3>
      <p>Verwalte Aufgaben mit Fälligkeitsdaten, Prioritäten und Status. Verpasse nie mehr eine Abgabe.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">📅</div>
      <h3>Kalender &amp; Prüfungen</h3>
      <p>Behalte Prüfungsdaten im Blick. Der integrierte Kalender zeigt alle wichtigen Termine auf einen Blick.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">📄</div>
      <h3>Studiengänge-Import <span class="pro-badge">Pro</span></h3>
      <p>Importiere Module, ECTS und Prüfungstermine direkt von deiner FH — aktuell FFHS, BFH, ZHAW und weitere.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">⏱</div>
      <h3>Lern-Timer</h3>
      <p>Tracke deine Lernzeiten pro Modul mit dem integrierten Pomodoro-Timer. Sieh genau, wie viele Stunden du investierst.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🧠</div>
      <h3>Lernziele &amp; Spaced Repetition</h3>
      <p>Speichere Lernthemen mit Wissensstand und automatischer Wiederholungsplanung. Das System erinnert dich zum optimalen Zeitpunkt.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🗂️</div>
      <h3>Karteikarten &amp; KI-Import</h3>
      <p>Erstelle Karteikarten manuell oder lade ein Dokument hoch — unsere KI generiert automatisch Lernkarten. Mit Spaced-Repetition-Algorithmus für optimales Lernen.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
      <h3>Noten, ECTS &amp; Statistiken</h3>
      <p>Verfolge deine Noten, berechne den gewichteten Durchschnitt und sieh wie deine bestandenen Noten automatisch ECTS-Credits gutschreiben.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🗺️</div>
      <h3>Studienplan</h3>
      <p>Deine Semester-Roadmap auf einen Blick: Module pro Semester, ECTS-Fortschritt, Pflicht- vs. Wahlmodule — alles visuell aufbereitet.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">📋</div>
      <h3>Timeline</h3>
      <p>Alle Aufgaben und Prüfungen chronologisch sortiert. Überfällige Einträge werden markiert — damit du nichts verpasst.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🕐</div>
      <h3>Stundenplan (KW-basiert)</h3>
      <p>Wöchentlicher Stundenplan als Raster (7–20 Uhr) mit Kalenderwochen-Tabs. Einträge per Klick anlegen, Farben wählen — übersichtlich wie auf Papier.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">💬</div>
      <h3>KI-Studien-Coach <span class="pro-badge">Pro</span> <span style="background:#F3F4F6;color:#6B7280;font-size:.63rem;font-weight:700;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:100px;white-space:nowrap;">nur Desktop</span></h3>
      <p>Stell dem integrierten KI-Coach Fragen zu deinen Modulen. Er kennt deine Lernziele und gibt gezielte Lerntipps. Aktuell exklusiv in der Desktop-App.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── WIE ES FUNKTIONIERT ───────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="steps-section">
  <p class="section-label">So einfach geht's</p>
  <h2 class="section-title">In 3 Schritten startklar</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">Kostenlos registrieren — keine Kreditkarte nötig. Web App sofort, Desktop-App jederzeit.</p>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">1</div>
      <h3>Konto erstellen</h3>
      <p>Registriere dich in 30 Sekunden unter <strong>app.semetra.ch</strong> — oder lade die Desktop-App herunter und melde dich dort an.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">2</div>
      <h3>Studiengang wählen</h3>
      <p>Wähle deine Fachhochschule und deinen Studiengang — alle Module werden automatisch importiert (Pro). Oder füge sie manuell hinzu.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">3</div>
      <h3>Studium im Griff</h3>
      <p>Aufgaben, Prüfungen, ECTS — alles auf allen Geräten synchron. Das Dashboard zeigt deinen Fortschritt.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

